title: MUMBLE_SET_VOLUME_OVERRIDE_BY_SERVER_ID
content:
0xCE8E25B4// MumbleSetVolumeOverrideByServerId
void MUMBLE_SET_VOLUME_OVERRIDE_BY_SERVER_ID(int serverId, float volume);Parameters:serverId: The player's server id.volume: The volume, ranging from 0.0 to 1.0 (or above).Overrides the output volume for a particular player with the specified server id and player name on Mumble. This will also bypass 3D audio and distance calculations. -1.0 to reset the override.
